sequenceDiagram
  participant U as user
  participant H as Harness
  participant C as Capability Catalog
  participant M as Model
  participant S as Skill Runtime
  participant P as Tool Pipeline

  U->>H: Fix test failure
  H->>C: Query related skill index
  C-->>H: test-fix / code-review summary
  H->>M: Task + Light SkillIndex + Minimal Tool
  M-->>H: intent: load_skill(test-fix)
  H->>S: Verify permissions and render Skill
  S-->>H: Skill body and running boundaries
  H->>M: Inject Skill Guide
  M-->>H: intent: Bash(npm test)
  H->>P: Unified execution pipeline
